    "body": "`interpolate` shares a code path with `fillna` [here](https://github.com/pydata/pandas/blob/b585b5ae3901aee8625e45f030d341db768ad8ad/pandas/core/internals.py#L877), where we try one of the fillna methods, and if the `method` isn't valid e.g. `linear` we try an `interpolate` method.\n\nMight need to flip the `axis` argument [here](https://github.com/pydata/pandas/blob/b585b5ae3901aee8625e45f030d341db768ad8ad/pandas/core/internals.py#L909).\n@EVaisman interested in submitting a fix and some tests?\n"
